{
  "stem": "10181.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the Dutch policeman said, I-- I guess he doesn't want to go on this train.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the-- the German policeman said to [? the guard, ?] then take him off immediately.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's too much commotion, you know, and I don't like it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I was taken off the train together with my cousin and put aside, you know, till the train left.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were kept in sort of a holding place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were some other people taken off the train, too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I wasn't the only one, but they were taken for different reasons.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were taken off because at the last moment, the commandants decided that their deferment was still good and they shouldn't go, or they had good connections with-- with-- with the Jewish commandant-- there was a Jewish commandant, too.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And maybe he knew them and tried to get them off.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So a few other people were taken off because they were privileged.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I was taken off with my cousin because I'd screamed-- for no other reason.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Of course, this-- I found out years later, this particular train went to Sobibor and nobody survived.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Nobody came back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Very few Jews survived Sobibor.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You know that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Sobibor was a death camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There was no selection like in Auschwitz, there was just-- this was just a death camp, and-- and a majority of people were taken straight to the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And-- and there were no known survivors of this particular transport.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So if I wouldn't have screamed, I wouldn't be sitting here today.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "That's-- I always tell this to people, and that's the strange quirks of life sometimes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You know, the little things make, you know, make big differences in your life, and this was one of the little things, to scream, and it made all the difference.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
